snippet.title: Thank You - Jason Kelce Officially Retires
snippet.description:
After 13 season as the Philadelphia Eagles' starting center, Jason Kelce is officially retiring from the NFL. One of the greatest of all time, Kelce finishes his career as a seven-time Pro Bowler, six-time First-Team All-Pro, and most importantly, a Super Bowl Champion, helping bring the City of Brotherly Love its first Super Bowl victory during the historic 2017 season.

Jason Kelce has shown the football world what it means to be an Eagle throughout the entirety of his years in Midnight Green. Congratulations on an incredible run, Jason. Thank you!

#Football #NFL #Eagles
